name: Falafel Wrap
shortDescription: Crispy falafel balls wrapped in pita bread.
details: Crispy falafel balls made from ground chickpeas and herbs, wrapped in warm pita bread. Served with creamy tahini sauce, fresh lettuce, and tangy pickles for a perfect balance of flavors.

name: Tacos Al Pastor
shortDescription: Spicy pork tacos with pineapple and cilantro.
details: Tender, marinated pork cooked on a vertical spit, served on soft corn tortillas. Topped with sweet pineapple, fresh cilantro, and a squeeze of lime for a burst of flavor.

name: Burger Deluxe
shortDescription: A juicy beef burger with lettuce, tomato, and cheese.
details: Made with 100% organic beef, this burger features a juicy patty, crisp lettuce, ripe tomatoes, and melted cheese, all served on a freshly baked bun. Perfectly paired with golden fries.

name: Pasta Alfredo
shortDescription: Creamy Alfredo sauce with fettuccine pasta.
details: Silky smooth Alfredo sauce made with Parmesan cheese, butter, and cream, tossed with perfectly cooked fettuccine pasta. Garnished with a sprinkle of parsley for a touch of freshness.

name: Churros with Chocolate
shortDescription: Sweet fried dough with cinnamon sugar and chocolate dip.
details: Freshly fried churros, crispy on the outside and soft on the inside, dusted with cinnamon sugar. Served with a rich, velvety chocolate dipping sauce for the ultimate treat.

name: Sushi Platter
shortDescription: A variety of fresh sushi rolls with soy sauce and wasabi.
details: A beautifully arranged platter of sushi rolls, featuring fresh fish, avocado, and cucumber, wrapped in vinegared rice and nori. Served with soy sauce, wasabi, and pickled ginger.

name: Pad Thai
shortDescription: Stir-fried rice noodles with shrimp and tofu.
details: Authentic Pad Thai made with stir-fried rice noodles, succulent shrimp, and crispy tofu. Tossed in a tangy tamarind sauce and garnished with crushed peanuts, fresh lime, and bean sprouts.

name: Chicken Biryani
shortDescription: Spicy chicken biryani with basmati rice.
details: Fragrant basmati rice layered with tender, spiced chicken, caramelized onions, and aromatic spices. Slow-cooked to perfection for a rich and flavorful experience.

name: Caesar Salad
shortDescription: Classic romaine lettuce with parmesan and croutons.
details: Crisp romaine lettuce tossed with creamy Caesar dressing, topped with grated parmesan cheese, crunchy croutons, and grilled chicken for added protein.

name: Greek Salad
shortDescription: A refreshing mix of tomatoes, cucumbers, and feta.
details: Fresh tomatoes, cucumbers, red onions, kalamata olives, and creamy feta cheese, drizzled with extra virgin olive oil and oregano for a Mediterranean taste.

name: Cobb Salad
shortDescription: A hearty mix of chicken, eggs, avocado, and bacon.
details: A filling salad featuring grilled chicken, crispy bacon, hard-boiled eggs, creamy avocado, cherry tomatoes, and blue cheese crumbles on a bed of fresh greens.

name: Quinoa Salad
shortDescription: Protein-packed quinoa with fresh veggies and herbs.
details: A nutrient-dense salad with fluffy quinoa, cherry tomatoes, cucumbers, bell peppers, parsley, and a zesty lemon dressing.

name: Caprese Salad
shortDescription: Tomato, mozzarella, and basil drizzled with balsamic glaze.
details: Juicy tomatoes, creamy mozzarella cheese, and fresh basil leaves drizzled with a tangy balsamic glaze and extra virgin olive oil.

name: Waldorf Salad
shortDescription: A fruity mix of apples, walnuts, and grapes.
details: A light and refreshing salad made with crisp apples, juicy grapes, crunchy walnuts, and celery, all tossed in a creamy mayonnaise dressing.

name: Kale & Cranberry Salad
shortDescription: Superfood salad with kale, cranberries, and nuts.
details: A healthy mix of kale, dried cranberries, toasted almonds, and feta cheese, tossed in a light lemon vinaigrette.

name: Asian Sesame Chicken Salad
shortDescription: Crisp greens with grilled chicken and sesame dressing.
details: A delicious salad featuring grilled chicken, fresh lettuce, shredded carrots, crispy wonton strips, and sesame seeds, served with a tangy sesame-ginger dressing.

name: Avocado & Chickpea Salad
details: A refreshing blend of ripe avocado, protein-packed chickpeas, diced cucumbers, cherry tomatoes, and a zesty lime dressing.

name: Beet & Goat Cheese Salad
shortDescription: Earthy beets paired with tangy goat cheese.
details: A beautiful combination of roasted beets, creamy goat cheese, candied walnuts, and arugula, served with a light balsamic dressing.
